          <div class="post-heading">
            <h1>Salmon Meets A Bad Man</h1>
            <h2 class="subheading">A man named after a fish finds it hard to be human.</h2>
            <span class="meta">Written by
              <a href="#">Juliet Lacey</a>
              on October 27th, 2018</span>
